episodes.title: Unveiling the Secrets of Cults: A Captivating Interview with David Lane by Greg Vlamis, Part One
episodes.description:
Unveiling the Secrets of Cults: A Captivating Interview with David Lane by Greg Vlamis, Part One 
 Unveiling the Secrets of Cults: A Captivating Interview with David Lane by Greg Vlamis, Part One 
Part one of a nine part interview of David Lane conducted by Greg Vlamis which touches upon John-Roger Hinkins, MSIA, Eckankar, Radhasoami, Shabd Yoga, Faqir Chand, Darwin Gross, Paul Twitchell, Harold Klemp, Indian gurus, inner visions, Ken Wilber, Da Free John, Sai Baba, and more, which was conducted in 1988 in Del Mar, California

A Rough Water Product
